article_title: U.S. Judge Joel Dubina Visits Enterprise
article_text:
One of the nation's most well known and respected federal judges visited the City Of Progress today.

The Honorable Joel Fredrick Dubina was the guest speaker at the Enterprise Rotary Club.

He is the chief judge for the u-s court of appeals for the eleventh circuit court based in Atlanta.

He discussed several high profile cases he presided over including the American Affordable Care Act... Often referred to as Obamacare.
